  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is to investigate the effect of Victoza (a GLP-1 receptor agonist)on
      insulin-dose, risk of hypoglycemia and gastric emptying rate during hypoglycemia in patients
      with type 1 diabetes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
